The article announces several nominations and appointments for various positions within the US government. These include Frank T. Brogan being nominated for Assistant Secretary for Elementary and Secondary Education, Lisa Gordon-Hagerty being nominated for Under Secretary for Nuclear Security, Andrea L. Thompson being nominated for Under Secretary of State for Arms Control and International Security, and Susan A. Thornton being nominated for Assistant Secretary of State (East Asian and Pacific Affairs). These nominations are replacing individuals who have either resigned or are resigning from their positions.